  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/SystemConfiguration\/kSCCompAnyRegex-swift.var\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:08:29Z\n---\n\n# kSCCompAnyRegex\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nA regular expression pattern that matches any component.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet kSCCompAnyRegex: CFString\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThis constant represents the regular expression pattern `[^\/]+`.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecConnectTime**: The IPSec key ConnectTime.\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecRemoteAddress**: The IPSec key RemoteAddress.\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecStatus**: The IPSec key Status.\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecXAuthEnabled**: The IPSec key XAuthEnabled.\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecXAuthName**: The IPSec key XAuthName.\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecXAuthPassword**: The IPSec key XAuthPassword.\n- **kSCPropNetIPSecXAuthPasswordEncryption**: The IPSec key XAuthPasswordEncryption.\n- **kSCPropNetProxiesProxyAutoConfigJavaScript**: The Proxies key ProxyAutoConfigJavaScript.\n- **kSCResvInactive**: The reserved key __INACTIVE__.\n- **kSCResvLink**: The reserved key __LINK__.\n- **kSCValNetIPSecAuthenticationMethodCertificate**: The constant value Certificate.\n- **kSCValNetIPSecAuthenticationMethodHybrid**: The constant value Hybrid.\n- **kSCValNetIPSecAuthenticationMethodSharedSecret**: The constant value SharedSecret.\n- **kSCValNetIPSecLocalIdentifierTypeKeyID**: The constant value KeyID.\n- **kSCValNetIPSecSharedSecretEncryptionKeychain**: The constant value Keychain.\n\n",
